raffle_Lottery_prizeiPhone16ProDesc: This is not just a smartphone, it's your new navigator, a stylish companion, and a personal office in your pocket. We're giving away the iPhone so your trips with us will be not only comfortable but also super-technological. Stay on the wave of innovation — with us and your brand-new iPhone!
raffle_Lottery_prizeAirPodsMaxDesc: Maximum comfort, style, and sound! AirPods Max is like first class in headphones. Immerse yourself in your own world of music and enjoy every detail while we take care of your journey.
raffle_Lottery_prizeAirPodsDesc: Style, quality, and freedom of sound! AirPods are your perfect companion for music and communication. Enjoy effortless use and crystal-clear audio wherever you go.
raffle_Lottery_prizeAirPodsProDesc: Nothing sounds as cool as traveling with us and music in your AirPods Pro! With noise cancellation, crystal-clear sound, and comfort, it's the perfect companion for your journey. A gift that fits every step and trip you take!
raffle_Lottery_prizeAirTagDesc: Your belongings will never be lost again, just like you won’t get lost with our taxi! AirTag is your personal detective, always knowing where your keys, bag, or suitcase are. Reliability and peace of mind — the ideal addition to our innovative trips!
raffle_Lottery_prizeBottleDesc: Stay hydrated in style with ShuttleX! This sleek and practical bottle reminds you that with us, you always reach your destination. Water inside is always a great idea, just like a trip with ShuttleX!
raffle_Lottery_prizeDeskLampDesc: Light that guides the way! Our lamp is a unique accessory with a city route-inspired design. It will brighten your space and add an adventurous touch to your home.
raffle_Lottery_prizeHoodieDesc: Incredibly comfortable, this hoodie will keep you warm on even the most unexpected routes. Featuring a city map design, it reminds you that all roads lead to ShuttleX. The perfect choice for stylish travelers!
raffle_Lottery_prizeTshirtDesc: Light, breathable, and stylish — the ShuttleX T-shirt will be your guide to comfort. Its minimalist design speaks for itself: you’re always on the right path.
raffle_Lottery_prizeMugDesc: Warmth on the go and at home! The ShuttleX mug with premium tea is made for enjoyable moments and planning your next adventure.
raffle_Lottery_prizeToteBagDesc: Stylish and spacious! The ShuttleX tote bag, designed with a city motif, is the perfect companion for any journey or daily task. Convenient, fashionable, and always ahead of the curve!
raffle_Lottery_prizeBagDesc: Designed for an active lifestyle and travel! The ShuttleX bag combines sleek style and functionality, making it your reliable companion for any occasion.
